-- LDK Gets CBD Approval for Loans to Fund California Solar Projects
-- B y   B a l d a v e   S i n g h
-- 2012-01-04T08:55:04Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-04/ldk-gets-cbd-approval-for-loans-for-california-solar-projects.html
China Development Bank Corp. has
approved a 15-year project loan for Co.’s 8 megawatts of solar
 power plants  in  California , according to a statement from LDK
today. 
• CDB also approved a fifteen-year buyer’s credit to LDK unit
KDC Solar LLC for its two New Jersey solar power plants,
totalling 14.7 megawatts of capacity
• CDB also approved two-year construction financing loan to EPC
contractor,  Solar Power Inc. (SOPW) , which is majority owned by LDK, to
construct the New Jersey plants
• The loan amounts weren’t disclosed  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Baldave Singh at 
 bsingh35@bloomberg.net  